tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits except for a slightly decreased HbA1c (3.9%), which may suggest recent hypoglycemia or low average glucose levels. Renal function, electrolytes, and glucose are normal. No acute laboratory abnormalities detected; clinical correlation is recommended.
